程序包 net.opentsdb.query.expression

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    Expression
    The interface for various expressions/functions used when querying OpenTSDB.
    ITimeSyncedIterator
    An interface for expressions or queries that operate across time series and require point-by-point timestamp synchronization.
    VariableIterator
    An interface that helps merge different time series sets (e.g. different metrics with a group by operator).
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    Absolute
    Modifies each data point in the series with the absolute value, tossing away the signed component.
    Alias
    Returns an alias if provided or the original metric name if not.
    DiffSeries
    Performs a UNION set join on up to 26 metric query results and returns the difference.
    DivideSeries
    Performs a UNION set join on up to 26 metric query results and returns the quotient.
    EDPtoDPS
    An ugly temporary class for converting from an expression datapoint to a standard data point for serialization in the default query format.
    ExpressionDataPoint
    Contains the information for a series that has been processed through an expression iterator.
    ExpressionFactory
    A static class that stores and instantiates a static map of the available functions.
    ExpressionIterator
    A iterator that applies an expression to the results of multiple sub queries.
    ExpressionReader
    Parses a Graphite style expression.
    Expressions
    Static class with helpers to parse and deal with expressions
    ExpressionTree
    A node in a tree of nested expressions.
    HighestCurrent
    Implements top-n functionality by iterating over each of the time series, sorting and returning the top "n" time series with the highest current (or latest) value.
    HighestCurrent.MaxLatestAggregator
    Aggregator that stores only the latest value for each series so that they can be sorted on it
    HighestMax
    Implements top-n functionality by iterating over each of the time series, finding the max value for each time series within the query time range, and up to "n" time series with the highest values, sorted in descending order.
    HighestMax.MaxCacheAggregator
    Aggregator that stores the overall maximum value for the entire series
    IntersectionIterator
    This class handles taking a set of queries and their results and iterates over each series in each set with time alignment after computing the intersection of all sets.
    MovingAverage
    Implements a moving average function windowed on either the number of data points or a unit of time.
    MultiplySeries
    Performs a UNION set join on up to 26 metric query results and returns the product.
    NumericFillPolicy
    POJO for serdes of fill policies.
    NumericFillPolicy.Builder
    A builder class for deserialization via Jackson
    PostAggregatedDataPoints
    A class to store an array of data points processed through expressions along with the original meta data of the result set (metric, tags, etc).
    Scale
    Multiplies each data point in the series by the given factor.
    SumSeries
    Performs a UNION set join on x metric query results and returns the results.
    TimeShift  
    TimeSyncedIterator
    Holds the results of a sub query (a single metric) and iterates over each resultant series in lock-step for expression evaluation.
    UnionIterator
    An iterator that computes the union of all series in the result sets.
  • 枚举概要 
    枚举 说明
    VariableIterator.SetOperator
    An operator that determines how to sets of time series are merged via expression.
